results.description:

In GOD WAR, the Fantastic Four find themselves stranded in another dimension, hunted by the warriors from the dread world of Acheron – and its ruler, Thanos, won’t rest until he possesses the one weapon which will give him dominion over the entire cosmos: the mind of young Reed Richards! Continuing their greatest hits streak on the The World's Greatest Comic Magazine!, Stan Lee and Jack Kirby weren't content just to create the Inhumans, Galactus, and the Silver Surfer.
